summary: An email from the FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking unit, dated July 21, 2021, transmitting a brief overview and two indictments related to the Ghislaine Maxwell case. The email offers to provide additional information.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: The subject of the two attached indictments transmitted by the FBI. The email is related to her criminal case.

events.title: FBI transmits Maxwell case documents
events.description: The FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking unit sends an email with a case overview and two indictments against Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: The FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking unit was actively managing the Ghislaine Maxwell case as of July 2021.
The communication involved transmitting at least two indictments against Ghislaine Maxwell.
The email indicates an ongoing legal process and information sharing related to the Maxwell prosecution.
